    • apply

      public AlertBuilder apply(Consumer<Alert> func)
      Applies a function to the Alert instance currently being built. Most operations on the instance can be performed using this method.

      Example usage:

      
 apply(alert -> alert.setId("Main" + alert.getTypeSelector()))
      Returns:
      builder instance
